overview.en: One Genesis is an ecological public chain of the origin of the evolutionary era。It was originally founded by a group of faiths around the world. The blockchain technology is launched by geeks,and this cross-age concept is gradually being used by major traffic communities, media,and eyes. Recognized by high-level investment institutions and traditional financial associations with strong financial resources. Gradually formed an episode of influence,Technology,flow,and financial resources are the core four-dimensional integrated consensus project.
overview.zh: One Genesis 是一个自进化划时代起源生态公链，最早由一群世界各地信仰 BTC的区块链技术极客发起，这种跨时代的理念逐渐被各大流量社群、媒体、眼光极高的顶级投资机构、财力雄厚的传统商会联盟所认可。逐渐形成了一个集影响力、技术、流量、财力为核心的四维一体的超级共识项目。
